Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西元2167年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球因为超新星爆炸\N遭受到巨大的灾害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.70,0:00:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过世界上的人们\N同心协力面对这场灾难
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的大家 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球现在很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过得也还算好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是西元2356年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望天际  满天繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞往通向明日的灿烂大道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱内心的蓝天  go far away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:01:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯了总是羡慕别人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得自豪的自己逐渐远去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍动无形之翼  我们展翅高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生而为人因此能描绘梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望天际  满天繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞往通向明日的灿烂大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.48,0:01:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱内心的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.25,0:01:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将能摆脱懦弱的自己奔驰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来请无限延伸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,go far away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(210,340)\fs22\shad0}第８话  是我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚任务的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力指向能量装置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类史上最大的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.74,0:02:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要进入关键时分了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有考虑过会失败吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然相信就不需要根据了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰好快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰最近真努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近还一个人作无重力练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一步！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2分20秒 今天的最高记录
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰好厉害 赢大小姐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还差一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳学姐在预科生的记录\N是2分5秒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这该不会是向对手宣言吧？\N-别这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 现在不是在上格斗技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面两个怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来会是4分多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更新最高记录之后\N最低记录也要更新了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是星之道的宇宙服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2分5秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平了最高记录？\N跟初佳一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:04:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宾果 正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪边来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发翘成圆形耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像洋娃娃一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然顺序反了 不过介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是转学生…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风祭玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从最远的究极基地过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫玲奈耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从究极基地来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人从那么远的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她虽然才12岁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过成绩非常优秀\N所以被编为预科生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然年纪很轻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JOJO 她的实力可比你好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要拿我比啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这里就由…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风祭回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照克尔纽曼的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑洞会回转并且带有电荷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极基地还没有成立学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以上课很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.06,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能那么拿手\N我也会很快乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别嫉妒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不是输给玲奈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要这么说的话大家都输啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才果然是存在的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是赢不过天才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完饭之后有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吃完之后跟我比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚任务的辅助成员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像会从星之道的正科生\N选六个人出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果四个是我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有草薙叶子 珠华铃\N或者是仁科优子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对 预科生也可以列入候补
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是在宇宙球赛有点活跃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打赌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不值得赌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极基地周边似乎\N确认有不明飞行物体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以风祭技术官\N才把女儿送到这里是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚任务都要开始了说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为要开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先接触二次冲击的究极基地\N现在都是报导媒体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易被反对运动盯上的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭思想跟命运论者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明人类面临危机\N为什么就没办法团结呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类要互相理解是很难的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学生如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如传闻中的天才少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在预科生里头名列前茅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为很好的刺激了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人反而泄气就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的成绩是B级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOOD  A级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的成绩是A级
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 是A级 我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就三连胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要比什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是赢不了你呢 玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你可以这么拿手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我做过很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多次？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 从小时候就做很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住在基地的时间比\N住在地球上的时间还来的长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎都是住在基地里头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极基地没有多少小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且大人都很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我常常玩那些模拟器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零重力练习跟模拟器\N对我来说是生活的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以会拿手是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也算是偷跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈从很久以前就开始学了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能一开始就这么拿手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是初佳学姐也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰 你有打过雪仗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有看过雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球应该会下雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是每个地方都会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰住的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会下啊 我也打过雪仗喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想玩打雪仗之类的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找时间过来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候一起打雪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有雪屋 滑雪\N还有堆雪人通通可以教你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我教你怎么玩宇宙滑板吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转弯的时候是有窍窍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰要像这样给它扭过去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 扭啊扭的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭啊扭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭啊扭？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭啊扭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭啊扭扭啊扭~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在进行\N重力指向能量装置的展开作业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B区以外都禁止进入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我会小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是要自己练习
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是向前看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会向前就一直向前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会向后就一直向后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子要多看两边比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信时而出现时而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉幅度变化太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样在自我陶醉\N以及消极之中反覆来回
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以让自己的器量变大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们年轻人就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（闪电交锋）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人一开始就会拿手的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然现在做不到\N就要练习到下次做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次跟初佳比赛时…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要赢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  弥生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到小碰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得她说要练习闪电交锋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟机器练习很无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要获得老师的许可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再讲就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的成绩是S级
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么\N这次用究极基地的玩法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 不沿着路线跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得了十分钟的话就攻守交换
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小碰 我要继续啰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蕾拉老师叫来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连预科宿舍长也得去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了一个转学生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是跳级进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩当然很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许跟以前的你有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚任务的辅助成员定案了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望身为宿舍长的你们\N可以帮忙公布内容
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一个人写五张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是海报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是传统啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练机？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该是禁止进入吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要张开啰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（主引擎破损）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作业区域有训练机？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 有一台是究极基地的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风祭吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈 快阻止机身飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去会撞到能量装置的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在做 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法阻止吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法接收我们这边的讯号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近只有片濑志麻的训练机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快准备救护艇\N-是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是究极基地的训练机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手好像是小碰喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.21,0:16:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去40秒之后就会撞到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要在那之前\N让玲奈转搭这台训练机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（成功机率8％）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 失败的话玲奈就会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练机里头至少有安全装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许只会受到轻伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰 这边看来完全不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果我没有接到的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我办不到的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是小碰的话\N一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级射球员片濑志麻\N你可是我的对手喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会来星之道就是因为有小碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了跟小碰比赛\N所以我才选星之道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那种实力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟玲奈或初佳比的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰不相信自己吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信自己的话就相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信把小碰当成对手的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信让小碰成为\N宇宙球赛选手的老师们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信迷上小碰演出的那些观众
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信小碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算要去救她？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.32,0:17:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败的话两个人都会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓准时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次 要冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 速度太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定会处罚你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天先好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚啰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有好消息要告诉英雄小碰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么消息？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰被选上成为\N浩瀚任务的支援成员了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害喔 小碰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就说过 小碰很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星之道总共六个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分别是四天王跟小碰 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音山光太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他会被选上？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法接受吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的成绩只有C级
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正科生里头也有人平均A级啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所有的成绩都是C级
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是平均
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困难的课题跟简单的课题都是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这或许只是个巧合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那给你看个有趣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音山光太的视野能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道这能力有多好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音山光太 非常恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S级 您的成绩是S级
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓死我啰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到会被选为辅助成员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没有自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么又说这种话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以近距离看到二次冲击喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是很光荣的事情\N所以就尽管高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.59,0:21:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生的话请说名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的话就直接进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地来这里说这句话？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教 我的对手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教 我的室友！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:22:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是仰望着闪亮的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要得到翅膀高飞俯瞰天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来无论为何都将来访
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望看到无人曾见的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.87,0:22:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道何谓停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本不安的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就任凭自己拥抱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破涕而笑时总会想起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以活着的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类就像是五彩缤纷的繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是装饰精美的绮丽夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的我又再次仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚任务终于来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为学生的我\N只能躲在避难所里面
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被选上支援任务的小碰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见不到究极基地双亲的铃奈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然平常都是大而化之
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种时候却没办法出力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集的宇宙学园\N「启程出发」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰 路上小心喔


